To build the FAT jars, use this command inside of each service folder.
for example: Microservices-with-kubernetes\Chapter12\microservices\product-service

docker-compose build --no-cache --> for no cache build

Command --> mvn clean package spring-boot:repackage

For recommendation service:
Do a clean first in the main parent pom
then do
mvn compile
then inside the microservices/recommendation folder
do this : mvn package spring-boot:repackage


Review Service Pom:

Agar ReviewMapperImpl generate nahi hui, to iska matlab MapStruct annotation processor run hi nahi hua jab aapne project build kiya.

ye pom.xml kaafi clean hai, bas ek important cheez missing hai —
MapStruct ka annotation processor Maven compiler plugin me explicitly declare nahi kiya gaya.

Is wajah se compile time pe ReviewMapperImpl.java generate hi nahi hota. Annotation processor ki classes
target/generated-sources/annotations mae hoti hain.

<plugins>
        <!-- ✅ Compiler plugin with MapStruct annotation processor -->
        <plugin>
            <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
            <artifactId>maven-compiler-plugin</artifactId>
            <version>3.11.0</version>
            <configuration>
                <source>${java.version}</source>
                <target>${java.version}</target>
                <annotationProcessorPaths>
                    <path>
                        <groupId>org.mapstruct</groupId>
                        <artifactId>mapstruct-processor</artifactId>
                        <version>${mapstruct.version}</version>
                    </path>
                </annotationProcessorPaths>
            </configuration>
        </plugin>

